Police at a California concert venue claim a woman was asked to move to a different area because her baby was at risk in the pit with her - though the woman claims it was because she was breastfeeding in public.

A video taken at a Brad Paisley concert on Thursday shows Chula Vista police speaking to 30-year-old mother Megan Christopherson, NBCLosAngeles reported, who was there with her baby and another daughter.

'My child that is actually sleeping and I'm getting escorted by police,' she says through tears as she is led out of the pit.Â 

